      • getOrphanParameters

        @Query(value="SELECT p FROM Parameter p, Node n INNER JOIN p.owner o LEFT JOIN n.refined n1 LEFT JOIN n1.refined n2 WHERE n.id = :node AND (o=n OR o=n1 OR o=n2) AND (p.mode = org.ligoj.app.api.SubscriptionMode.ALL OR p.mode = :mode) AND ((EXISTS(SELECT 1 FROM SystemRoleAssignment ra INNER JOIN ra.role r WHERE ra.user.id = :user     AND EXISTS(SELECT 1 FROM SystemAuthorization a WHERE a.role = r AND a.pattern = \'.*\'          AND a.type = org.ligoj.bootstrap.model.system.SystemAuthorization$AuthorizationType.API))) OR EXISTS(SELECT 1 FROM DelegateNode d WHERE (n.id LIKE CONCAT(d.name, \':%\') OR d.name=n.id) AND ((receiverType=org.ligoj.app.iam.model.ReceiverType.USER    AND receiver=:user)  OR (receiverType=org.ligoj.app.iam.model.ReceiverType.GROUP   AND EXISTS(SELECT 1 FROM CacheGroup cg   WHERE receiver = cg.id     AND EXISTS(SELECT 1 FROM CacheMembership cm INNER JOIN cm.group g WHERE cm.user.id = :user          AND (g.description = cg.description OR g.description LIKE CONCAT(\'%,\',cg.description)))))  OR (receiverType=org.ligoj.app.iam.model.ReceiverType.COMPANY AND EXISTS(SELECT 1 FROM CacheCompany cc WHERE receiver = cc.id     AND EXISTS(SELECT 1 FROM CacheUser cu INNER JOIN cu.company c   WHERE cu.id = :user          AND (c.description = cc.description OR c.description LIKE CONCAT(\'%,\',cc.description)))))))) AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM ParameterValue WHERE parameter = p AND (node=n OR node=n1 OR node=n2)) ORDER BY UPPER(p.id)")
java.util.List<Parameter> getOrphanParameters(java.lang.String node,
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        org.ligoj.app.api.SubscriptionMode mode,

        Return all parameters associated to a node but without specified value for the given node or its parent. The parameters are filtered by the requested mode. Also check the node is visible for the given user.
        Parameters:
        parent - the parent node identifier.
        mode - Expected mode.
        user - The user requesting the nodes.
        Returns:
        all parameters associated to a node but without a value.

        @Query(value="SELECT p FROM Parameter p, Node n INNER JOIN p.owner o LEFT JOIN n.refined n1 LEFT JOIN n1.refined n2 WHERE n.id = :node AND (o=n OR o=n1 OR o=n2) AND (p.mode = org.ligoj.app.api.SubscriptionMode.ALL OR p.mode = :mode) AND ((EXISTS(SELECT 1 FROM SystemRoleAssignment ra INNER JOIN ra.role r WHERE ra.user.id = :user     AND EXISTS(SELECT 1 FROM SystemAuthorization a WHERE a.role = r AND a.pattern = \'.*\'          AND a.type = org.ligoj.bootstrap.model.system.SystemAuthorization$AuthorizationType.API))) OR EXISTS(SELECT 1 FROM DelegateNode d WHERE (n.id LIKE CONCAT(d.name, \':%\') OR d.name=n.id) AND ((receiverType=org.ligoj.app.iam.model.ReceiverType.USER    AND receiver=:user)  OR (receiverType=org.ligoj.app.iam.model.ReceiverType.GROUP   AND EXISTS(SELECT 1 FROM CacheGroup cg   WHERE receiver = cg.id     AND EXISTS(SELECT 1 FROM CacheMembership cm INNER JOIN cm.group g WHERE cm.user.id = :user          AND (g.description = cg.description OR g.description LIKE CONCAT(\'%,\',cg.description)))))  OR (receiverType=org.ligoj.app.iam.model.ReceiverType.COMPANY AND EXISTS(SELECT 1 FROM CacheCompany cc WHERE receiver = cc.id     AND EXISTS(SELECT 1 FROM CacheUser cu INNER JOIN cu.company c   WHERE cu.id = :user          AND (c.description = cc.description OR c.description LIKE CONCAT(\'%,\',cc.description)))))))) AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM ParameterValue WHERE parameter = p AND node.id != :node AND (node=n OR node=n1 OR node=n2)) ORDER BY UPPER(p.id)")
java.util.List<Parameter> getOrphanParametersExt(java.lang.String node,
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                org.ligoj.app.api.SubscriptionMode mode,

        Return all parameters associated to a node but without specified value for the given node's parents. The parameters are filtered by the requested mode. Also check the node is visible for the given user. Parameter having a value associated directly to the given node will be returned. This is the sole difference with getOrphanParameters(String, SubscriptionMode, String)
        Parameters:
        parent - the parent node identifier.
        mode - Expected mode.
        user - The user requesting the nodes.
        Returns:
        all parameters associated to a node but without a value.

      • findOneVisible

        @Query(value="FROM Parameter p INNER JOIN p.owner n WHERE p.id=:id AND ((EXISTS(SELECT 1 FROM SystemRoleAssignment ra INNER JOIN ra.role r WHERE ra.user.id = :user     AND EXISTS(SELECT 1 FROM SystemAuthorization a WHERE a.role = r AND a.pattern = \'.*\'          AND a.type = org.ligoj.bootstrap.model.system.SystemAuthorization$AuthorizationType.API))) OR EXISTS(SELECT 1 FROM DelegateNode d WHERE (n.id LIKE CONCAT(d.name, \':%\') OR d.name=n.id) AND ((receiverType=org.ligoj.app.iam.model.ReceiverType.USER    AND receiver=:user)  OR (receiverType=org.ligoj.app.iam.model.ReceiverType.GROUP   AND EXISTS(SELECT 1 FROM CacheGroup cg   WHERE receiver = cg.id     AND EXISTS(SELECT 1 FROM CacheMembership cm INNER JOIN cm.group g WHERE cm.user.id = :user          AND (g.description = cg.description OR g.description LIKE CONCAT(\'%,\',cg.description)))))  OR (receiverType=org.ligoj.app.iam.model.ReceiverType.COMPANY AND EXISTS(SELECT 1 FROM CacheCompany cc WHERE receiver = cc.id     AND EXISTS(SELECT 1 FROM CacheUser cu INNER JOIN cu.company c   WHERE cu.id = :user          AND (c.description = cc.description OR c.description LIKE CONCAT(\'%,\',cc.description))))))))")
